					<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p><a href="/wiki/index.php/Musicproduction:Main" title="Musicproduction:Main">Music Production main page</a>&#160;: <a href="/wiki/index.php/Musicproduction:daw" title="Musicproduction:daw">DAW specifics</a></p>
<p>LMMS is an Open Source projet, which allow you to produce music with your computer. This includes the creation of melodies and beats, the synthesis and mixing of sounds, and arranging of samples. You can have connecty your MIDI-keyboard. The interface is user-friendly.</p>
<p>It runs on Linux but you can find binaries for Windows.</p>
<p>Some recording and post recording options are missing but can be done with another Open Source projet, Audacity. </p>
