<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Project_specifics">Project specifics</span></h2>
<p>details of file management
<ul><li>Project Name
<ul><li>A project file is stored in a mmp or mmpz. LMMS can import MIDI and FLP (Fruityloops Project) files directly.
</li></ul>
</li><li>File type
<ul><li> Project can be exported to wav or ogg file but can use mp3, au, SoundFont2 (SF2 Player), VSTi (VeSTige), LADSPA, GUS patches (PatMan) and MIDI files.
</li></ul>
</li><li>Bit depth
<ul><li> The primary bit depths in LLMS are 16 and 32.
</li></ul>
</li><li>Sampling rate
</li><li>Hardware
<ul><li> LMMS can interact with MIDI keyboard.
</li></ul>
</li><li>Buffer size
<ul><li> The default buffer size is 256 frames but can be tuned.
</li></ul>
</li><li>Project folders specifics</p>
</li></ul>

